We gaan bowlen.

696
00:51:52,776 --> 00:51:54,569
Was dat The Big Lebowski?

697
00:51:55,737 --> 00:51:56,571
Ja.

698
00:51:57,114 --> 00:51:58,323
Klaar?
-Ja.

699
00:51:58,406 --> 00:51:59,241
Vooruit.

700
00:52:58,175 --> 00:53:01,803
Je bent schattig. Kom op.

701
00:53:01,928 --> 00:53:02,804
Wacht. Ik…

